description: Try this honey soy chicken stir-fry recipe for dinner tonight. It's quick, easy and packed with colourful veg.
name: Honey Soy Chicken Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500 g chicken breast or thigh fillets

recipeInstructions.text: Stir honey soy mixture, then add to frying pan. Simmer, stirring for 2 minutes or until chicken is cooked through and vegetables are tender-crisp. Serve with rice and garnish with extra green onions.
